# The locations, geographic features, and other points of interest for map B3.

Toepia
    floating town, NW lake
    bridge connecting to Brittle

Brittle
    floating town, W lake
    bridge connecting to Toepia

Rack
    floating town, E lake

Jamn
    floating town, S lake

Razor demon
    lives in lake
    like Oriental dragon, long and sinewy, but also has razors or scales or something

Lake
    consumes 75% of B3
    two rivers leave through the E, one NE and one SE
    one river enters from the NW
    whirlpool in center

Citadel
    supported by a column seated to the lake bed, through the center of the whirlpool

